\c 21
\s Dhavhidhi anotizira Nobhi kuna Akishi paGati
\p
\v 1 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakauya kuNobhi kuna Ahimereki mupristi\x + 22.9,11,19. Neh. 11.32. Isa. 10.32.\x*; Ahimereki ndokudedera pakusangana naDhavhidhi; ndokuti kwaari: Sei iwe uri woga, uye kusina munhu anewe\x + 16.4.\x*?
\v 2 Dhavhidhi ndokuti kuna Ahimereki mupristi: Mambo wakandiraira basa, uye wakati kwandiri: Ngakurege kuva nemunhu anoziva chinhu chipi nechipi chebasa randinokutuma naro, nerandinokuraira. Uye majaya ndaazivisa zvenzvimbo yakadai neyakadai.
\v 3 Zvino ikozvino, chii chiri pasi peruoko rwako? Ipai muruoko rwangu zvingwa zvishanu, kana zvingawanikwa.
\v 4 Mupristi ndokupindura Dhavhidhi ndokuti: Hapana chingwa chakajairika pasi peruoko rwangu, asi pane chingwa chitsvene\x + Eki. 25.30. Rev. 24.5. Mat. 12.3,4. Mako 2.25,26. Ruk. 6.3,4.\x*; koga kana majaya akazvichengeta pavakadzi\x + Eki. 19.15. Rev. 15.18. Zek. 7.3.\x*.
\v 5 Dhavhidhi ndokupindura mupristi ndokuti kwaari: Zvirokwazvo vakadzi vakadzivirirwa kwatiri mazuva angava matatu pakubuda kwangu; uye nhumbi dzemajaya itsvene, asi neimwe nzira \add chingwa\add* chakajairika\x + Rev. 8.26.\x*, uye pamusoro peizvi, nokuti nhasi chaitwa chitsvene panhumbi.
\v 6 Naizvozvo mupristi wakamupa \add chingwa\add* chitsvene, nokuti paiva pasina chingwa ipapo, kunze kwechingwa chekuratidza, chaiva chabviswa pamberi paJehovha, kuti kuiswe chingwa chinopisa nezuva rekubviswa kwacho\x + Rev. 24.9.\x*.
\v 7 Zvino kwaiva ipapo neumwe wevaranda vaSauro nezuva iroro akabatirirwa pamberi paJehovha\x + 21.5.\x*, zvino zita rake raiva Dhoegi muEdhomu, mukuru wevafudzi vaiva vaSauro\x + 22.9.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Dhavhidhi ndokuti kuna Ahimereki: Kuti pano hapana pfumo kana munondo pasi peruoko rwako here? Nokuti zviri zviviri munondo wangu nezvombo zvangu handina kuzvitora muruoko rwangu, nokuti basa ramambo nderekukurumidza.
\v 9 Mupristi ndokuti: Munondo waGoriati muFirisitia\x + 17.51.\x* wawakauraya mumupata weEra\x + 17.2.\x*, tarira, wakaputirwa mumucheka seri kweefodhi; kana uchida kutora iwo, tora, nokuti hapana umwe kunze kweiwoyo pano. Dhavhidhi ndokuti: Hakuna wakadaro, ndipe iwo\x + 31.10.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakasimuka ndokutiza nezuva iro kubva pachiso chaSauro, akaenda kuna Akishi mambo weGati\x + 17.4.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino varanda vaAkishi vakati kwaari: Uyu haasi Dhavhidhi mambo wenyika here? Havana kuimba umwe kune umwe pamusoro pake\x + 18.7.\x* mukutamba here vachiti: Sauro wakauraya zvuru zvake, asi Dhavhidhi makumi ezvuru zvake\x + Vato. 21.21.\x*?
\v 12 Dhavhidhi ndokuisa mashoko awa mumoyo make, ndokutya kwazvo Akishi mambo weGati\x + Ruk. 2.19.\x*.
\v 13 Zvino wakashandura kuzvibata kwake pamberi pemeso avo, ndokuedzesera \add kuva\add* benzi paruoko rwavo, akakwara-kwara pamagonhi esuwo, akarega mate ake achisiririka pandebvu dzake\x + Map. 34.\x*.
\v 14 Zvino Akishi wakati kuvaranda vake: Tarirai, munoona kuti munhu uyu ibenzi; mamuunzirei kwandiri?
\v 15 Ndinoshaiwa mapenzi kanhi, zvamaunza uyu kuti apenge pamberi pangu? Uyu achapinda mumba mangu here?